	 * @param	X			X position of the triangle
	 * @param	Y			Y position of the triangle
	 * @param	Height		Height of the triangle
	 * @param	FillColor		The ARGB color to fill this triangle with. FlxColor.TRANSPARENT (0x0) means no fill.
